    <main>
      <h2>Representing destinations</h2>
      <p>The way bottom navigation destinations are represented can depend on how many are used:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Three destinations: </strong><a href="index.html">Display icons and text labels</a> for all destinations.</li>
        <li><strong>Four destinations: </strong> Active destinations display an icon and text label. Inactive destinations display icons, and text labels are recommended.</li>
        <li><strong>Five destinations: </strong> Active destinations display an icon and text label. Inactive destinations use icons, and use text labels if space permits.</li>
      </ul>
    </main>
